sources.description:
The Merry Gentleman - A woman leaves an abusive husband to start a new life in Chicago, where she befriends a man undergoing an emotional crisis, who she does not know is a professional killer, and a detective, who is investigating the hit man.
2008.  Stars: Michael Keaton, Kelly Macdonald, Bobby Cannavale
